text:
Submitted by admin on 10/21/2015 @ 5:16 AM Companies mentioned in this article: Ticket Down 
NEW YORK, Oct. 21, 2015 /PRNewswire-iReach/ -- Ticket Down is a reputable source of authentic 5 Seconds of Summer tickets for their blockbuster 2016 "Sounds Live Feels Live Tour" summer concert tour. This past Friday was a glorious day for 5 SOS fans in North America. The band released it's new music video "Hey Everybody!" and also announced a blockbuster summer amphitheater tour which will visit countless outdoor venues along with some indoor venues during the summer months of 2016.

The tour gets underway on July 1st at the Mohegan Sun Arena in Uncasville, CT and it goes on until September 18th and culminates at the The Woodlands Pavilion.
